\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus opened his eyes as the Guide woke him from his well earned nap. He sat up and stretched, feeling much improved, but not nearly back to fully rested. At least his resource pools were full and he could string two thoughts together in a way that made sense.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 As soon as his eyes focused on her, the Guide began speaking to him. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The next evaluation cycle will be focused on Wisdom. Since you have proven to be a prodigy in Mana Control and have already learned Basic Meditation, your evaluation will be unique to you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s eyes went wide and he swallowed. He remembered quite well the steep increase in difficulty his final cycle had experienced in the first evaluation for similar reasons. \u8220\'93Okay, how rough is this going to be?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You will spend the first portion of the cycle on a complex mana manipulation problem meant to push your understanding of and ability to control mana,\u8221\'94 she answered. \u8220\'93The problem will require focus and attention to detail, but is certainly within your demonstrated capabilities. After that, I will spend the remainder of the cycle assisting you with further developing and evolving your meditation technique.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That doesn\u8217\'92t sound too bad,\u8221\'94 he relaxed a little. \u8220\'93Can you explain the mana problem?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I can,\u8221\'94 she nodded. \u8220\'93Five mana spheres will manifest in the room, each with a different affinity. You will be given a short window to explore these spheres and identify their affinities. That window will end with a stream of mana being injected into the room. This stream will extremely dense and comprised of mana of all five affinities in randomly varying concentrations. Your task is to separate out the incoming mana into it\u8217\'92s different affinities and feed the appropriate affinity mana to each of the spheres.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93A mana, sorting problem then?\u8221\'94 he clarified.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Essentially yes,\u8221\'94 she nodded. \u8220\'93You will be judged on your ability to correctly funnel mana into the spheres without absorbing and purifying any of the mana meant for the spheres.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Oh,\u8221\'94 Marcus\u8217\'92s eyes widened somewhat. \u8220\'93So I\u8217\'92m not just sorting the five affinities for the spheres but also moving anything that doesn\u8217\'92t belong to the spheres through my core to purify it\u8230\'85 That is a bit more complicated since I will have to consciously monitor my own mana intake as well.\u8221\'94 He nodded. \u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s doable though.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The Guide nodded. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93This portion will end when mana remains that matches the affinity of the spheres.\u8221\'94}
